about.summary: Python requests like API built on top of Twisted's HTTP client

name: treq
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "treq" %}
{% set version = "18.6.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "91e09ff6b524cc90aa5e934b909c8d0d1a9d36ebd618b6c38e37b17013e69f48" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - setuptools
    - incremental
  run:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - requests >=2.1.0
    - twisted >=16.4.0
    - incremental
    - six
    - attrs

test:
  imports:
    - treq

about:
  home: https://github.com/twisted/treq
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Python requests like API built on top of Twisted's HTTP client"
  doc_url: http://treq.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/twisted/treq

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - synapticarbors
